text: The Giro dell'Emilia Internazionale Donne Elite is a women's staged cycle race which takes place in Italy and is currently rated by the UCI as category 1.Pro.Giro dell'Emilia Internazionale Donne Elite 2018 (1.1) on Cycling Fever. ==Overall winners== ==References== Category:Women's cycle races Category:Cycle races in Italy
